Matteo Capucci (he/him) renamed stream seminar: YAMCaTS to event: YAMCaTS.

*** Yorkshire and Midlands Category Theory Seminar
*** Thursday, 25th January 2024
*** University of Leeds

The 33rd meeting of the Yorkshire and Midlands Category Theory Seminar (YaMCATS) will be held at the University of Leeds on 25th January 2024. The speakers will be

Clark Barwick (University of Edinburgh)
Ana Ros Camacho (University of Cardiff)
Giacomo Tendas (Masaryk University / University of Manchester)

Please check the YaMCATS website

https://conferences.leeds.ac.uk/yamcats/

for further information.

YaMCATS is a research network involving the Universities of Leeds, Manchester and Sheffield, supported by the London Mathematical Society.

With best regards,
Nicola Gambino (University of Manchester), also on behalf of Jo√£o Faria Martins (University of Leeds) and Markus Szymik (University of Sheffield)
If you wish to attend YaMCATS 33 (Jan 25th, 2024, University of Leeds), please register via the website https://conferences.leeds.ac.uk/yamcats/ by Monday 22nd January, 5pm in the UK.
